## BallerApp

- **App**: court discovery, ranked games, tournaments
- **Flutter**: `baller_app/pubspec.yaml` (SDK `^3.9.0`) · Maps · geolocator
- **Backend**: `backend/app/main.py` FastAPI + PostGIS (`docker-compose.yml` at repo root)
- **Entry**: `baller_app/lib/main.dart` → `BadwordFilter` → `AuthGate()`
- **Data layer**: `baller_app/lib/repositories/` · `baller_app/lib/core/api/` (API mode) · legacy `lib/supabase/court_services.dart`
- **Design**: `baller_app/DESIGN.md` · `baller_app/lib/design_system/` · `baller_app/baller-design-knowledge.md` · `.cursor/project/design-pipeline.md`
- **CI**: `.github/workflows/pr-quality.yaml` (`peakoss/anti-slop@v0`)

